y an ABG within 21&#x02013;30 dB (10%) and 31&#x02013;40 dB (10%) (<xref ref-type="table" rid="T4">Table.4</xref>).</p><table-wrap id="T4" position="float"><label>Table 4</label><caption><p>Pre- and post-operative ABG in Group B</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups"><thead><tr><th style="background-color:#D9D9D9;" align="left" rowspan="2" colspan="1">
